  "name": "Valkyries",
  "content": "# Valkyries\n\nOdin's warrior maidens who select fallen heroes from battlefields to bring to Valhalla. Divine shield-maidens who serve the Einherjar mead and decide the fates of warriors in combat.\n\n## Abilities and Powers\n\n- Brynhildr: The most famous Valkyrie, punished by Odin for disobeying him, placed in an enchanted sleep surrounded by fire until awakened by Sigurd\n- Göndul: A war Valkyrie who decides battles\n- Skögul: Another battle Valkyrie, companion of Göndul\n- Hildr: \"Battle\" - leads the eternal battle of Hjadningavig\n- Geirahöd: \"Spear of Battle\"\n\n## Archetypal Significance\n\nValkyries guide the worthy dead to their afterlife destination - divine beings who choose fate in battle.\n\n",
